  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink114">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi koṇka</l>
<l>nērē māyiṉuñ celkuvaṅ kollō</l>
<l>kaṭali ṉārai yiraṟṟu</l>
<l>maṭalam peṇṇaiyava ṉuṭaiya nāṭṭē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh friend, listen!</l>
<l>Even if we do not come face-to-face with the man from the sea,</l>
<l>Won’t we go to his land [with] Palmyra trees with fronds,</l>
<l>Among which wader-birds shriek?</l>
</lg>
    </div>
